ara": "Hyderabad's government is cracking down on illegal construction waste dumping. New rules now mandate developers to manage demolition debris responsibly, requiring undertakings against illegal dumping and proof of recycling partnerships. Large construction projects and road works must now incorporate recycled C&D waste, promoting sustainable practices and cleaner urban spaces across key municipal areas.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/infrastructure/telangana-government-takes-strong-action-against-illegal-cd-waste-dumping/131888560?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-95740/131888560.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "infrastructure"}]}